{
  "stem": "20978.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the ghetto in general, very crowded, very crowded, very fearful.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Especially if you were-- if you come from a family with a little bit of wealth.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Germans or the Hungarians would come into the ghetto every day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they'll take people that, that had businesses and take them out in a van where you don't see them-- in an enclosed van-- and torture them to get their money that they're-- if they have any fortune hidden-- gold.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when they brought them back, they were either mentally unable to function or physically unable to function from the beating that they took.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was also one of the reasons that my father left.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father left before the Germans came into Hungary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, he didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At that time, no, he didn't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] My mother, you know, made him leave as soon as he could, you know.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because God knows what would have happened if he stayed there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because he was a well-known person, a respected citizen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he would have been probably-- maybe would have been tortured.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't know-- I mean, he heard whatever he heard on the radio in America in Brooklyn.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he didn't know where we were, whether we were in Auschwitz or whether we were alive, until we got back to Hungary.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the ghetto, there wasn't a great shortage of food.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We had bread and meat, you know, because we, we stored up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We stocked up on things-- and flour.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you baked-- you did your own baking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, they, they set up sort of a makeshift hospital.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was in-- one of the houses was an apartment house.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
